{"tid":1716735,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"之前報夢巴夢境提及廢棄站 點解冇人提幽靈車站：古洞站？","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T12:16:51.000Z","uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2143956a10048fbc05ebb2b68234a9d93ea186","tid":1716735,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3mtR2X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3mtR2X.png&h=a2b01bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【失蹤11年】港商返港再失蹤 流浪2日徘徊古洞巴士站<br />\n<br />\n在東莞露宿街頭達11年的68歲港商陳志健，經中國義工協助下，上周四(3日)返港與家人團聚。消息透露，陳返港後，獲送往北區醫院跟進健康狀況，但陳其後再度失去蹤影。及至今日凌晨，終由巡警在上水青山公路古洞段一巴士站，發現他在上址徘徊，經查證，獲悉他正是失蹤人士，遂將其送返北區醫院。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20170806/57048304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170806%2F57048304&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0Qq7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=b8f913ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170806%2F57048304&h=0bd0723e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20170806/57048304</a><br />\n<br />\n個個都話個富商傻左 但點解佢要由灣仔去到咁遠徘徊？<br />\n老人痴呆都可以重提舊日重要嘅舊事 古洞應該有特別事件令富商返去<br />\n<br />\n我睇大家討論報夢巴嘅車站 都冇提過古洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重要係富商係俾人捉過去送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以抛出黎睇下 設施都幾齊全 會唔會用來收野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53abf44e275c7c8c116d4a01e21ddda1f08198ab","tid":1716735,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"又要查案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}